  "title": "Site Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate and communicate with architects, consultants, subcontractors and suppliers regarding technical matters and to ensure project specifications are meet.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate and instruct supervisors to carry out assigned projects to ensure timely completion as per schedule.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with clients, architects, engineers and other stakeholders to ensure smooth project execution.</li>\n  <li>Assist in the planning and scheduling of construction activities.</li>\n  <li>Conduct site inspections to ensure compliance with safety and quality standards.</li>\n  <li>Monitor project progress and provide regular updates to the project manager.</li>\n  <li>Attend project meetings and provide updates on construction progress and challenges.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Civil Engineering or related field.</li>\n  <li>At least 2-5 years working experience in a related industry.</li>\n  <li>Good team player and problem solver.</li>\n  <li>Candidate must be open for 5.5 days work</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
